{"tid":1592613,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國脫歐大轉折：最高法院判決首相暫停議會不合法","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:45:28.000Z","uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3478eef7591b2f714c53ebd097e659e55dae74b3","tid":1592613,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:40:47.000Z","msg":"英國脫歐大轉折：最高法院判決首相暫停議會不合法<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/904/cpsprodpb/170A4/production/_108927349_301e3a91-401b-4d78-a0d9-7f898922a1a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F904%2Fcpsprodpb%2F170A4%2Fproduction%2F_108927349_301e3a91-401b-4d78-a0d9-7f898922a1a7.jpg&h=1b485073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國最高法院大法官黑爾宣佈裁決：首相約翰遜暫停議會的做法&quot;不合法&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n英國最高法院周二（9月24日）裁決，首相鮑里斯&middot;約翰遜暫停議會五星期的舉措「不合法」。<br />\n<br />\n經首相約翰遜提議、英國女王批准， 英國議會罕見地被暫停五個星期，從而使議會在10月31日脫離歐盟最後期限之前，喪失關鍵的討論和決策時間。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜政府說，選擇暫停議會，是因為約翰遜在7月底剛剛出任首相，現政府需要制定新計劃和議程。<br />\n<br />\n但是，英國最高法院裁決，讓議會無法「盡職責」是錯誤的。<br />\n<br />\n英國最高法庭大法官黑爾（Lady Hale）在宣佈裁決時表示，(暫停議會)的舉措「給民主基礎帶來的影響極大」。<br />\n<br />\n黑爾說，11位法官一致認定，暫停議會的決定「無效」，下院議長和上議院將決定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-49811779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-49811779&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=b4d8ccf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-49811779&h=c2c6797b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-49811779</a>"},{"pid":"c38e3f01050b3b41eb91f6eff9d89dd90af14691","tid":1592613,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"ef90e3021a72d4fefbac13b90ace8cf02cc52f10","tid":1592613,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"比起脫唔脫歐家陣咁搞法分分鐘變憲政問題"}]}